
# dctemplates, dftemplates

These sources are from: http://www.netlib.no/netlib/templates/index.html

No license agreement could be found in the source archives for
dctemplates/dftemplates, however, permission was granted via email by
the author, Jack Dongarra, to incorporate into Siconos or any other
package under the terms of the Modified BSD license (also known as
3-clause BSD license), reproduced below.

Statement from Jack Dongarra via personal communication with Stephen
Sinclair, April 5, 2018:

